Comment: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:53.35,Ristorante,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Flavor of Orsini

Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.50,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:33.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I often see you here, so I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:36.42,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,My father is buried here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.81,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to be rude, but may I ask your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:55.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You must have lost someone very dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:00.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.40,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're ready to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:04.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,We have to mail all the invitations out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:56.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,This mysterious restaurant is on a road just a little ways from the center of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.94,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:09.89,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rizzo, a regular, promised to bring him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.96,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Senator Fassone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He... He's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:26.66,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Just when I was starting to think better of her, she acts like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.98,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is nice to see the Madam in good spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.05,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.79,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.50,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The owner is in the back. Take this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:43.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't get her obsession with gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.18,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.49,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You used to the place yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.36,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The owner really does look so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.78,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,"Why Olga of all people?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:03.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,...et cetera, is what I'd like to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I've never really talked to Gigi either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think he dislikes me or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.55,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He tipped me off on how to sneak in free dolces...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What a peculiar man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.43,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a read on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:46.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was born in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fassone must be tired from working in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.42,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:54.68,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we give him something, on the house, to let him relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,A Piemonte red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.97,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I picked it up on my last day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go very well with his primo course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.78,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one! I knew you'd come through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.44,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep doing whatever you want, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.30,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Some might call that abuse of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:30.70,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you like bespectacled men, that's just playing favorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's not playing favorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:39.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,As the proprietress of this establishment, it's my duty to see that our customers are satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.74,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.50,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:04.36,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,See? Gigi's a real pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:10.48,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Without you saying a word, he'll pick the exact wine that you're craving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta, when you're done with that, bring the owner's dishes back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.00,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,His next course is about ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:30.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:38.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He comes to refill his glass even though he can't see him drinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.52,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He knows the pace I normally drink at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Have you known Gigi a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.49,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, he's been here since the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:52.40,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Look at the second picture from the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That was taken twenty-seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:05.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That was taken when my brother and I opened the ristorante next to the winery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The precursor to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.53,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I manage a winery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.44,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I-I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.92,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you are brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.11,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.03,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Half-brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:25.42,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... No wonder you've known each other so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.18,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:32.43,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But we met when I was twenty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.28,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,A wine connoisseur that I knew introduced us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I was visiting a home in the suburbs of Turin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gian Luigi Orsini...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:49.97,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.50,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Right. My father told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, big bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.79,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What are you running off for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:15.93,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.60,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My father says we aren't to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:30.66,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. You're brothers, but you weren't allowed to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi and I share the same mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.53,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My father managed a winery outside of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:43.17,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi's father was a successful businessman in his hometown of Turin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:49.43,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So, I was born here and Gigi was born over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.22,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.67,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,These two are actually brothers, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:02.44,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So to me, he's both my half-older brother and my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.65,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:10.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. My father slept with his older brother's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.86,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to have such an interest in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.92,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you are a talented lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.74,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,so I suppose I shouldn't have assumed otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.93,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Table four is asking for the check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.35,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What a fascinating restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.76,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,staffed by nothing but men in spectacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:53.28,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This was actually a gift the owner made to his beloved wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:58.74,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm blessed to have met such a wonderful husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.75,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.58,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:11.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, so Gigi and your mother, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:17.18,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well before Gigi and I ever met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:23.63,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle never forgave my father for what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:28.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He said that by sleeping with his own brother's wife, he severed all familial ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He cut all ties with me, that stupid older brother of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:45.47,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he's a sommelier. That's what was on his business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi, really? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:53.31,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop by the restaurant where he works, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.42,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.10,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, big bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.12,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My dad had a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,"Stop by anytime for a drink."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:27.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Look how you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he took a liking to our winery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.29,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He soon started coming there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He was a real character, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:41.46,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I started to like him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.77,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:51.92,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I had a brother like you all these years, and yet we spent them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had met you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:12.39,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We're not involved in our fathers' feud,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.50,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,so let's stay on good terms, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:34.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My father and I talked the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:39.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We tossed around the idea of opening a fun, little ristorante next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,to go along with the wine we're making.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:46.21,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd be willing, I could use your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,in making the wine list.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.19,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This is an outrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:57.04,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I made it very clear that you were not to meet with people from that household!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:00.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare get near him ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:01.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.36,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:07.47,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind to work in the ristorante that Lorenzo is opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.60,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.47,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:15.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You may have your feud, but it's got nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.62,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The only wine we drink is from Piemonte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Lorenzo's wines are just as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:21.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:37.60,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, my uncle always had a weak heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi asked their servant to confirm that he's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.47,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,and then called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I... killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.53,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing the circumstances, it sounds like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.22,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But we still need to ask him if he killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:09.92,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured we'll let him spend the night in jail, then take him home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:30.81,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we opened the ristorante a year later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.10,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Those were some times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.06,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:40.02,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.11,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.42,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Teo commented that you've been gone a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.03,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:51.21,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Was he telling you about Gigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.83,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea he was the owner's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:15:00.53,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gigi does the books every night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:05.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The owner operates the winery too, so he's quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He's eating a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He eats too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:27.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I don't think he does whatever he wants because they're brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:30.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'd be like that no matter where he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.99,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The owner's story makes me feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.42,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Grazie. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:39.58,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.67,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The Senator seemed satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He might come back someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.35,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing. I was just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.32,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But this might get us some good publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:54.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And not for the spectacles, but for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... Furio's cooking and Teo's dolces are already well-known in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.56,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.07,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, thanks, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:06.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The food was delicious today, as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.97,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Just the fact you eat it is thanks enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:14.09,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mommy really wants to get married to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:17.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,but he told me he won't get married to someone who's been divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So you understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:24.14,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand why the owner opposes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.92,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,His parents were like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:32.43,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,And two brothers with the same woman... I'd better stop this train of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:37.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't want the same thing to happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:47.31,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That label... That bottle's from the owner's winery, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:08.36,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's an '82. The year the ristorante opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:14.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, you have a phone call from Mr. Rizzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.67,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Grazie! Thanks for tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.31,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I wanted to tell you what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:24.31,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is a lively one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You're her daughter, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.42,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio wouldn't have told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.32,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that? We don't look alike at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.32,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You share the same smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.07,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.44,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.59,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:25.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He knows what wine people want to drink because he observes them closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.80,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Two brothers going after the same woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Love takes all shapes and sizes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.60,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:48.38,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the Senator stopped by, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.28,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,How did Olga react?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You know an awful lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:57.25,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't stop talking about it back in the office. It was nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:00.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Gabrielle? You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.32,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.96,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah, the Senator just left a little while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.74,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,but he was drop-dead gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you have a happy marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.98,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:47.39,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. I'm sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:50.37,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to live together in Palermo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:56.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So, I don't think you'll see me there very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,How does she know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:03.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I see him quite a bit. Whenever we're visiting the cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:08.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want my father to be lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:12.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,but am I being a bad daughter for moving so far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.65,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's happy for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.66,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,up in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:32.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I wish a life of eternal happiness for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.89,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to have fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:52.03,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The girls know what kind of guy I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,so only the ones looking for a good time approach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:59.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,When those women weren't around, I was completely alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:00.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I...
